Vodafone Germany Smartphone Users to Triple, Sueddeutsche Says

-- B y   R a g n h i l d   K j e t l a n d
-- 
2011-08-31T07:52:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/vodafone-germany-smartphone-users-to-triple-sueddeutsche-says.html
Vodafone Group Plc (VOD) ’s German unit
predicts the number of customers using smartphones will “at
least triple or even quadruple” in the next three years,
 Sueddeutsche Zeitung  reported, citing an interview with Chief
Executive Officer Friedrich Joussen.  Currently a fifth of Vodafone Germany’s customers use
smartphones, Joussen said, according to the newspaper. The CEO
also said the company now has 40,000 television customers.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ragnhild Kjetland in Frankfurt at 
 rkjetland@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
